					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6194585#post-4391518</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6194585/scp-3274#post-4391518</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2019 17:12:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>CountSwagula</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5624286</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Didn't have me until the final interview log. Felt pretty standard time travel sci-fi up until the last log. Then it felt like a solid SCP.</p> <p>The first signs of things being off, the &quot;&#8230;fine surgical scarring along the cranium&#8230;&quot;, was great.</p> <p>&quot;Serve the Foundation and tell us how to stop this thing.&quot;</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
