						 <p>Saw the picture and thought, &quot;That guy's hair looks pretty Keter.&quot;</p> <p>You need to make it clear in the description that these people are amnesticizing themselves. It sounds like the Foundation was catching them and wiping their memories, which made understanding the whole article really difficult.</p> 
